Project Name: Guess the Number (Number Guessing Game)
Project Description: The player guesses a random number within a specified range. The system provides "bigger/smaller" hints based on the player's input until the correct number is guessed.
Basic Functions: 
Generate a random number (between 1 and 100) 
Input box and "Submit" button 
Real-time feedback: Too large / Too small / Congratulations
Enhanced features: 
Scoring: Record the number of attempts 
Limitations: If the request is made more than N times, a failure message will be displayed. 
Prompt system: Provides proximity indication
